Organics:

Organics tried to sooth the baby, but to no avail.  She then began to 
search the mess hall for anything the baby might eat.  She found a 
few bottles and formula.  She also found jarred baby food, in case 
she didn't want the bottle.  She gathered it all up and brought it ot 
the table.  She made up the formula and poured it into a bottle.  she 
then presented it to Elita, hopeful it would please her.
"Here you go, a bottle, just you asked, I hope."
